+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
                            PSYCHOMETRY
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

	Level: 9
	Cost: 100
	Text: psychometry <object>

	By reaching out your mind to bond with an object you will be
	able to learn things about that object. You will be able to
	tell if the object is a good weapon or if it would be worth
	a lot. Many things can be learned by the use of this power.

+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
